songs.title: Crazy Girl
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
How do you do it? How do you do these things to me?
You're like a magician, I can tell you got tricks up your sleeve
You're like a bull fighter, you got me feeling all riled up, feisty
Like a punk rocker, you make me want to break things

[Chorus]
How do you do it, do it, do it, do it?
How do you do it, do it, do it to me?
You make me feel giddy and meticulous
You make me feel a million different things
You make me into a crazy, crazy girl, girl, girl
Crazy girl

[Verse 2]
I need a straight jacket whenever I get around you
Cause you're like a magnet, I can't help it, I have to touch you
You're a dirty pirate, that's what I love about you
I don't feel worthy, you give me something to bow down to

[Chorus]
How do you do it, do it, do it, do it?
How do you do it, do it, do it to me?
You make me feel giddy and meticulous
You make me feel a million different things
You make me into a crazy, crazy girl, girl, girl
Crazy, crazy girl

[Bridge]
You make me act a little insane
You impair my judgment, you infect my brain
Like a hallucinogenic, an amphetamine
You really know how to get to me

[Chorus]
How do you do it, do it, do it, do it?
How do you do it, do it, do it to me?
You make me feel giddy and meticulous
You make me feel a million different things
You make me into a crazy, crazy girl, girl, girl
